        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099061 replaced by GO:0098839" , "Rationale: shisa9 is highly enriched in PSD subcellular fractions from adult mouse forebrain. Fluorescence microscopy demonstrates postsynaptic co-localization with gria1 and gria2/3 in mouse cultured hippocampal neurons at 20 days in vitro.\n\n\"integral component\" was Inferred from the protein's transmembrane domain.. Experimental description: Figure 2 literal;\n\"Immunoblots for CKAMP44, TARP-g-2, GluA1, PSD95, and Synapsin (Syn.) of\nsubcellular fractions from adult mouse forebrain homogenate\"" ;
